{"title_page": "Seanice Kacungira", "text_new": "{{short description|Ugandan journalist}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n'''Seanice Kacungira''' is a Ugandan [[journalist]] and [[radio personality]].\n\n== Work experience ==\nShe worked for Kenyan (Capital FM) and Ugandan Media (Sanyu FM, WBS and NTV).\n\nSeanice and her younger sister [[Nancy Kacungira]] together  co-founded Blu Flamingo; a digital media management company.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sautitech.com/digital/ceo-seanice-kacungira-how-to-improve-your-networking-game/|title=CEO Seanice Kacungira: How to improve your networking game|date=2018-10-10|website=SautiTech|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-15}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y2-FIPGLQfw|title=Seanice Kacungira on launching a Ugandan digital agency & the tipping point for online advertising|last=|first=|date=Feb 10, 2014|website=Youtube|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-15}}</ref>\n\n== Awards ==\nShe was recognized as one of Africa's Most Influential Women in Business and Government.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sqoop.co.ug/201908/four-one-one/seanice-kacungira-wins-award-in-africas-most-influential-women-in-business.html|title=Seanice Kacungira wins Africa\u2019s Most Influential Women in Business Award \u2013 Sqoop \u2013 Get Uganda entertainment news, celebrity gossip, videos and photos|last=Kyomugisha|first=Mercy|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-15}}</ref>\n\n== Personal life ==\nShe is married  to Fabian Adeoye Lojede and a mother of two.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bigeye.ug/seanice-kacungira-welcomes-bouncing-baby-girl/|title=Seanice Kacungira welcomes bouncing baby girl. [Photo]|date=2017-05-22|website=BigEye.UG|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-15}}</ref> She later changed her name to Seanice Lojede after her marriage.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bigeye.ug/seanice-kacungira-now-married-photos/|title=Seanice Kacungira Is Now Married. [Photos]|date=2014-12-12|website=Big